-- Majority of Canadians Say G-20 Summit Security Costs Are Not Justified
-- David Scanlan
-- 2010-06-16T13:38:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/majority-of-canadians-say-g-20-summit-security-costs-are-not-justified.html

          
          
             About 78 percent of Canadians say
the estimated C$1 billion ($970 million) security costs to host
the G-8 and G-20 summits in Toronto and Huntsville, Ontario are
not justified, according to a poll released today by Angus Reid.  
          
          


  


        